## Permission kontrolü

Her korumalı endpoint için `Depends(require_permission("module.action"))`.

```python
# GOOD
@router.delete("/customers/{id}")
def delete(
    id: int,
    _: AuthPrincipal = Depends(require_permission(CRM_CUSTOMER_DELETE)),
    ctx: TenantContext = Depends(get_tenant_ctx),
    svc: CustomerService = Depends(),
):
    svc.delete(db, ctx.tenant_id, id)
```

`role_has_permission()` permission matrix'e (`app/core/permissions.py`) bakar; izinler string sabit olarak tanımlı.
